dcterms:description: The dataset contains time-series gaming indicators in distinct game genres coming from NetEase Games. For each game, there is a corresponding game update announcement data, which can be considered as interventions.
dcterms:title: Games Dataset

dcterms:description: This dataset simulates the combined effects of chemotherapy and radiotherapy in lung cancer patients. At each timestep, there are four treatment options: no treatment, chemotherapy, radiotherapy, combined chemotherapy and radiotherapy.
dcterms:title: Tumour Dataset
